data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Mirada! This stunning single-family home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing space for your family to grow and thrive.  Step outside into your own private oasis, complete with a beautiful custom pool and spa, allowing you to enjoy the outdoors in comfort and style. The master bedroom features a convenient door leading directly to the pool area, providing easy access for a refreshing swim or a relaxing soak in the spa. The fenced-in backyard ensures safety for your loved ones. Embrace sustainability with the energy-efficient solar power electric system, reducing your carbon footprint and saving on utility bills. The granite counters in the kitchen add a touch of elegance, while the tile floors throughout the home create a sleek and modern feel. The luxury vinyl wood-like floors in the bedrooms add warmth and charm to the space. The attached 2-car garage ensures convenience and security for your vehicles. The great location of this home offers stunning preserve views, allowing you to enjoy the beauty of nature right from your own backyard. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Mirada! Call today for your private showing! *** Please check out the confidentials on financing opportunities.***
